to train;
add patient[] dataset files under "data/train" directory
-also you can change the test dataset

run data.py
it will show "new_data" directory

-you can run model.py to see details about model

run train.py
- you can change the hyperparameters on train.py

after the training files,logs files are to be created.


to validate;
run eval.py
after that "results" folder are to be created.

to test;
add .dcm dataset in directory data/test/
run predict.py
after that "test" folder are to be created.


